title: How to Plan & HIt Your 2019 Goals

description:
Episode 527 - Want to get better at planning and hitting your goals? Well in this episode I break down the 10 categories of goals that you can have for your New Year's Resolutions and give you the 3 steps to make hitting your goals easier!
